column2: "No good. They saw through me. I even disguised my parameters...so why?"
"With calculating powers on par with the Akashic Record, it is no surprise they would see through your mimicry."
"As expected of our... Of something created by the Photoners."
"ARKS mobile weaponry are approaching. They must have traced us back from our teleportation coordinates."
"Hmhm. Do they plan to take their revenge?"
"Such overconfidence in the wake of their successes is exactly the sort of behavior one of their failures would exhibit."
"So not even that was enough... Order a full retreat!"
"Right! All units, retreat! I repeat, all units retreat!"
"Oho, another round of cat and mouse? ...Always playing the role of predator has begun to bore me."
